<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1401262-why-do-reviews-tell-us-what-the-book-is">Why do reviews tell us what the book is about? We know that from the jacket cover or from Amazon. I personally stop reading when you start off by telling me what the book is about.</a>
